room_title: Escape room "Z-Cape Z-51" by Escape Room Napa in Rohnert Park
room_description: A group of terrorist scientists have infiltrated a CDC secret labratory and created a VIRUS.  By accident the lead scientist became infected with the virus before he was able to finish the cure. To make matters worse he set a bomb to disperse the virus and decimate the surrounding civilian population. The infected are wreaking havok on the lab, can your team complete the research, cure the scientist, and disarm the bomb in time?
